name: Party With Undead Elvis
description: That’s right ladies and gentlemen, the King has risen!  And Party Bot and Party Cat are more then happy to show the undead party master some good times!  But beware, Little Bastard is looming over them in the background.   Featured as an 11″ x 17″ print.

name: "The Party Pack" (mini comic, music, sticker, and button)
description: "The Party Life" mini comic + original music soundtrack download + W.A.O. sticker + 1.25" pin "The Party Life" is a full color, 16 page epic adventure of how Party Bot meets Party Cat and they vow to always keep the party going no matter what. Born from the science experiment that killed off all the humans, Lord Bubble Face will try relentlessly to diffuse their party plans. Do not miss this first We Are Objects comic release!
